\import{macros}

\p{This tree records a bounded 48 hour interaction-region snapshot captured from local interaction systems and reduced to public aggregate shape. The private substrate stays local: no chat titles, room ids, bearer tokens, direct-message names, message bodies, or raw session paths are published here.}

